{"tid":507255,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無業漢保釋　禁足全港龜池","createTime":"2017-12-23T04:54:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-23T06:28:10.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"869556a07975d2cbb723a2086b2822b899b628cb","tid":507255,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T04:54:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171223/20253112\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171223%2F20253112&d=YMjKz3cQ%2Fky9YqE0tBko1uI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=27c92967\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171223%2F20253112&h=c51b5b2f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171223/20253112</a><br />\n<br />\n無業漢保釋　禁足全港龜池<br />\n<br />\n法庭   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171223/large/12075400.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171223%2Flarge%2F12075400.jpg&h=00a0c4c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n高等法院<br />\n<br />\n【涉虐殺10龜】<br />\n【本報訊】無業漢涉於東區醫院水池用鉛筆插穿10隻巴西龜的頸及口，其中6隻當場死亡，另有4隻亦因重傷而要人道毀滅。他被捕後一直還柙，昨於高院向法官申請保釋，最終法庭批准他以現金5,000元保釋，並下令他保釋期間不准到全港任何龜池，明言：「再犯就冇情講，即刻鎖你。」案件將於1月12日於東區法院再訊。<br />\n<br />\n稱「我好蠢」不記得報到時間<br />\n<br />\n滿頭灰白髮的被告蔡曼生（60歲）昨沒律師代表，他於今年11月2日被捕，及後一直還柙。被告於庭上對答遲緩，多次沒聽清提問。法官批准被告保釋的其中一項條件，是被告須每周到柴灣警署報到。但當法官要求被告重複報道時間時，被告卻稱「唔記得」，及後法官再耐心說一次報到時間，被告仍稱「唔記得」，並表示：「我好蠢㗎！」法官最終要法庭寫下報到時間及日期予被告記着。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：HCCP361/17<br />\n■記者蘇曉欣"},{"pid":"4996e1ce4c04d25c2132c007adff1163cafd490c","tid":507255,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T04:56:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e4780504c072e2599e179191448281960ec6f75","tid":507255,"uid":37431,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"